# Dastkaar Kashmir

A premium B2B marketplace connecting Kashmiri artisans and manufacturers with verified buyers worldwide вЂ” carpets, pashmina, walnut wood, copperware, papier mГўchГ©, and more, backed by AI-assisted discovery and translation.

This is a working Flask app: real signup/login (salted password hashing, session auth), real product and message persistence (JSON-backed, per-user), and live AI features (buyer recommendations, translation, market demand/insights, and an AI chat assistant) powered by Groq. Analytics remains a UI placeholder. Everything is server-rendered HTML (Flask + Jinja2) with a single global stylesheet and vanilla JS.

## Tech Stack

- **Flask** вЂ” routing, auth/session handling, and template rendering (`app.py`)
- **Groq API** вЂ” real AI calls behind buyer recommendations, translation, market demand/insights, and the AI chat assistant
- **JSON files** вЂ” lightweight persistence for users, products, and messages (no external DB required)
- **Jinja2** вЂ” templating, layout inheritance, and reusable macros
- **Vanilla CSS** вЂ” one global stylesheet, CSS custom properties for the design system, no framework
- **Vanilla JS** вЂ” small, focused behaviors only (tabs, modals, password toggles, mobile drawer, chat, page-progress bar) вЂ” no build step, no bundler

